wstic\n|type1-2=Psychic}}\n\n===Sprites===\n{{Spritebox/Header|type=psychic}}\n{{Spritebox/NA|gen=VI}}\n{{Spritebox/6|ndex=677}}\n{{Spritebox/7|ndex=677}}\n{{Spritebox/Footer|677|Espurr}}\n\n==Trivia==\n\n===Origin===\nEspurr appears to be based on a kitten, particularly the {{wp|Scottish Fold}} breed due to its curled ears and lilac coloring. It may also be inspired by {{wp|nekomata}}, who can come from cats who live many years until their tail splits and they gain supernatural powers, much like when Espurr evolves into {{p|Meowstic}}.\n\n====Name origin====\nEspurr is a combination of \'\'{{wp|Extrasensory perception|ESP}}\'\', \'\'{{wp|esper}}\'\', and \'\'purr\'\'.\n\nNyasper may be a combination of ニャー \'\'nyā\'\' (onomatopoeia of the sound cats make) and \'\'esper\'\'.\n\n==In other languages==\n{{Other languages|type=psychic|type2=psychic\n|ja=ニャスパー \'\'Nyasper\'\'|jameaning=From {{tt|ニャー \'\'nyā\'\'|meow}} and \'\'{{wp|esper}}\'\'\n|fr=Psystigri|frmeaning=From \'\'{{tt|psy|psychic}}\'\' and \'\'{{tt|mistigri|archaic term for cat}}\'\'\n|es=Espurr|esmeaning=Same as English name\n|de=Psiau|demeaning=From \'\'{{tt|Psycho|Psychic}}\'\' and \'\'{{tt|Miau|meow}}\'\'\n|it=Espurr|itmeaning=Same as English name\n|ko=냐스퍼 \'\'Nyaseupeo\'\'|komeaning=Transliteration of its Japanese name\n|zh_cmn=妙喵 \'\'Miàomiāo\'\'|zh_cmnmeaning=From {{tt|妙 \'\'miào\'\'|mysterious}} and {{tt|喵 \'\'miāo\'\'|meow}}\n|zh_yue=妙喵 \'\'Miuhmīu\'\'|zh_yuemeaning=From {{tt|妙 \'\'miuh\'\'|mysterious}} and {{tt|喵 \'\'mīu\'\'|meow}}\n|hi=एसपर \'\'Espurr\'\'|himeaning=Transcription of English name\n|ru=Эспурр \'\'Espurr\'\'|rumeaning=Transcription of English name\n}}\n{{-}}\n\n==Related articles==\n* [[Students (Super Mystery Dungeon)]]\n\n==External links==\n\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Head|type=Psychic}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Pokémon|type=Psychic|prevnum=676|prev=Furfrou|nextnum=678|next=Meowstic}}\n|}\n{{Project Pokédex notice}}\n\n[[de:Psiau]]\n[[es:Espurr]]\n[[fr:Psystigri]]\n[[it:Espurr]]\n[[ja:ニャスパー]]\n